==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shēng mĭ zhŭ chéng shú fàn
===Etymology===
Literally: the raw rice has already been cooked.
===Idiom===
'''[[生]][[米]][[煮]][[成]][[熟]][[飯]]'''
# it is done cannot be undone; it is already too late to do anything about it
